description: Defines data models for a dictionary application, including DictionaryEntry, Phonetic, Meaning, and Definition classes, with functions for JSON parsing.

classes.name: DictionaryEntry
classes.description: Model representing a dictionary entry with properties like word, phonetics, and meanings, and a factory method for JSON deserialization.

classes.name: Phonetic
classes.description: Represents phonetic information including text and audio URL, with a factory method for JSON deserialization.

classes.name: Meaning
classes.description: Represents a word meaning with part of speech and definitions, with a factory method for JSON deserialization.

classes.name: Definition
classes.description: Defines a single word definition, optionally with an example, with a factory method for JSON deserialization.

methods.name: DictionaryEntry.fromJson
methods.description: Creates a DictionaryEntry instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: Phonetic.fromJson
methods.description: Creates a Phonetic instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: Meaning.fromJson
methods.description: Creates a Meaning instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: Definition.fromJson
methods.description: Creates a Definition instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: listFromJson
methods.description: Parses a JSON string into a list of DictionaryEntry objects.
